Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Layer:11 INFORNOGRAPHY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你來的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不必要在這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看見這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩倉玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟網上的玲音是同一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經在網上見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘綜合研究所的生化學基礎研究團隊成功地\N分析出染色體分子構造…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（玲音是偷窺者）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我才是真正的玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這真實的世界你已經沒有存在的價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自殺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？ 為何你要存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何要我去感覺你的存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯 我就是網上的神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音多和大家接觸比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真的變了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你又變回原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我們不好 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很累嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然自己直接接駁計算機登入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一併讀取所有數據是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在的狀況已經超過了你的界線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是機械吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我說成是機械一般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並沒有這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只不過是軟件的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 其實你只是個軟件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是硬件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軟件？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 是個執行程序 有肉體的軟件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:13:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千砂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千砂 你記得我們曾一起回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於明白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…你所說的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死是非常容易的 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死並不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 你已經有了死亡的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要解除手槍的保險制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對準目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用雙手扼緊 再有姆指按制開關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生的力量就夠用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣 你還留戀現實世界嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡滑了 是你叫我來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒有找過你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有肉體是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說法不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明天放學後大家集合見面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那男的真帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲 關於你和老師的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你找到了男朋友交往 那謠言就會不攻自破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明天再聊吧 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那事情是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰…誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼…你會變成這個…樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個並不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有偷看亞莉絲的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更沒有把秘密放在網上 我真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是玲音 一定是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我親眼目睹玲音偷看的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎不只有一個我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是另一個我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲也可能不只一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最多只能說不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓那件事就像沒發生過的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會努力做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經不需要任何道具了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:19:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡現實世界的分界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經可以隨意進入網絡界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是我出現在這裡的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那個謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定能使它變成不曾發生過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恐怖 太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲 早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼沒精打采？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道月事來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是不知羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉 今天我心情不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天收到一個很下流的電子郵件…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你撒謊 昨天我們還…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得今天你好像有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個老師很帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有傳言說他跟某高中三年級女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師和我的事不就沒有發生過？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟那老師有什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你也喜歡那位老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 你已經太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是 他已經有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 說話也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 快過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一點 快一點 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 她在笑
